videos.description: Sam Ehlinger looks for the hot route, but keeps it instead, breaks a tackle and runs in a 7-yard touchdown to put Texas on the board.
videos.headline: Ehlinger scores his 30th TD of the season

videos.description: Sam Ehlinger dumps it off to Keaontay Ingram who runs and scores an easy 19-yard touchdown to extend Texas lead to 14-0.
videos.headline: Ehlinger finds Ingram for the 19-yard TD

videos.description: Iowa State QB Brock Purdy rips a pass that bounces of the hand of his receiver and into the hands of Texas' Chris Brown deep in Iowa State's territory.
videos.headline: Purdy's INT gives Texas good field position

videos.description: Tre Watson finds the hole and bursts for a 39-yard gain to put Texas in Iowa State territory.
videos.headline: Watson erupts for a 39-yard run
